#### PR description:

Updating the import of fake Emtf params as [PR#29767](https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/29767) updates the module `fakeEmtfParams_cff.py` to `fakeEmtfParams_empty_cff.py` .
This can be considered as a follow up of [PR#29767](https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/29767).
